beer.beer_description: Escaping the realm of societal trends, we have challenged our curiosity with carefully structured microdoses of Riwaka, BRU-1, Citra and Columbus in an imperial West Coast style IPA. Our favourite WCIPA hops, blended together for the first time express free flowing earthy aromas heighten the senses whilst opening the gateway to a whole new world of complex citrus flavours and resin that are brought back to reality by an assertive bitterness and malty backbone. The perfect sipper for those looking to kick back, relax, and take a journey within their psyche.
